If you need urgent ceiling-light replacement for your office in Singapore, here are **three well-recommended service providers** that accept commercial/office jobs. I’ve included key details & tips for each so you can pick what fits best.

---

### 1. entity["turn0business28","Daylight Electrician Singapore",0]  
entity_metadata["turn0business28","one-line","Daylight Electrician Singapore",0]
image_group{"layout":"carousel","aspect_ratio":"1:1","query":["Daylight Electrician Singapore office light installation","Daylight Electrician Singapore commercial lighting work","Daylight Electrician Singapore electrician team on site"],"num_per_query":2}  
**Why they stand out:**  
- Offers a full range of lighting services including ceiling-light installation & replacement for commercial properties. citeturn0search2  
- They list “office light replacement” among their recent projects. citeturn0search2  
- Licensed electricians, relatively high review count (2,000+ reviews) at their address.  
**Tip for hiring:** Contact them for a quote and check whether they handle the particular ceiling-fixture model you have (or want). Ask for lead time for office hours so you cause minimal disruption.

---

### 2. entity["local_business","LS Handyman Singapore",0,{"location": ["Singapore, Singapore City, SG"]}]  
entity_metadata["local_business","one-line","LS Handyman Singapore",0,{"location":["Singapore, Singapore City, SG"]}]
image_group{"layout":"carousel","aspect_ratio":"1:1","query":["LS Handyman Singapore lighting installation office","LS Handyman Singapore ceiling light replacement","LS Handyman Singapore commercial lighting Singapore"],"num_per_query":2}  
**Why they’re a good option:**  
- They explicitly list “ceiling light”, “LED panel light replacement”, “downlight LED bulb replacement” among their services. citeturn0search1  
- Handyman service means they may be somewhat more flexible with scheduling urgent jobs.  
**Tip for hiring:** Confirm that the staff are certified/licensed for commercial electrical work (since “handyman” can sometimes imply residential only). Also verify after-job clean-up especially if your office space is live.

---

### 3. entity["local_business","Repair .sg",0,{"location": ["Mountbatten, Singapore, SG"]}]  
entity_metadata["local_business","one-line","Repair .sg",0,{"location":["Mountbatten, Singapore, SG"]}]
image_group{"layout":"carousel","aspect_ratio":"1:1","query":["Repair.sg light replacement commercial Singapore","Repair.sg ceiling light install Singapore office","Repair.sg urgent electrician Singapore"],"num_per_query":2}  
**Key points:**  
- They advertise same-day or next-day service for light repair/replacement jobs. citeturn0search9  
- Based at 229 Mountbatten Rd; could serve central Singapore offices.  
**Tip for hiring:** Because this is more of a general repair service, check whether they’ll provide a full replacement fixture (if needed) rather than just bulb/repair. Also check their quote includes any office-specific safety or disruption controls.

map

---

### ✅ Action Plan & Considerations

- **Scope**: Before contacting, identify how many fixtures need replacement, type of fixtures (flush-mount, panel LED, recessed, etc.), height of ceiling, and whether wiring needs updating.  
- **Schedule**: Since this is “urgent”, ask for availability during your preferred time (after business hours, weekend) to minimise disruption in office operations.  
- **Safety / Compliance**: Verify that the electricians are licensed for commercial work (check licences). Ensure they comply with Singapore’s electrical safety standards and building regulations.  
- **Quotation**: Ask for a breakdown: labour + fixture cost (if providing) + any lift/high-access charges + clean-up.  
- **Lead time & disruption**: If your office must stay operational, ask how they’ll stage the replacement to minimise loss of productivity (e.g., replace in batches, isolate zones).  
- **Warranty**: Check if there is some warranty or guarantee on workmanship and parts (especially if you’re installing new fixtures).  
- **Choice of fixture**: If you’re replacing existing units, decide whether you’re keeping the same style or upgrading (e.g., LED panel for energy efficiency). One of the providers (Daylight Electrician) mentions energy-efficient lighting options. citeturn0search2  

---

If you like, I can **scan and compile a list of 5-10 more providers** (with quotes, availability, compare prices) specialised in office/commercial lighting, and we can filter by your district (Singapore, e.g., Orchard, Raffles Place) and budget. Would you like me to do that?
